It sounds like an empty room.  A lot of echoes here.  I hope they continue to resound and people hear them.  It almost is like there was a frenzy prior to Memorial Day and now there is an exhausted feeling of burnout.  Is there nothing left?  Then again, it is summer and warmer and vacations and kids out of school.  Yes, Virginia, life does go on.  So folks, it's been enlightening.  I'm not leaving, I'm just watching more.
